fields.info: The library is operating in a fully automated environment. The library is using automation software. Library timings are 9.00 a.m to 6.00 p.m. Services provided are Document delivery service, Reference Service & Assistance Photocopy Service, Multimedia Resource On-line Databases, Current contents, User Education .

Information access, sharing and analysis are the key to teaching and learning process, Institute fraternity i.e. all students, teachers, staff departments and processes integrated round the clock. This integration is achieved through a strategic choice of partnering with industry leaders for leading edge technologies and utilizing them to their maximum. 

There is a regular update of computer hardware in the institute. At present, 60 desktop/laptop computers are allocated for use by students of various programme at the institute. Smooth functioning of these desktops/laptops is enabled through.

Class rooms are well ventilated with comfortable chairs. College classrooms are designed for discussions, and nearly every classroom incorporates technology. This means students in other countries can Skype into a U.S. classroom.

Our seminar halls are well-equipped with advanced sound systems and projector facilities that support proper training and lectures. Seminar halls are totally air-conditioned and hold a seminar hall capacity of more than 100 individuals. It also holds instruments that of the smart classrooms.

We also access our seminar halls at the time of the induction or orientation programme for freshers and when representatives of several conglomerates visit our college to enlighten the students on the requirements of the industry that guides their learning path.

Quality education and training along with student-centric facilities are all that we aim to offer. Hence, we strive to make the experience of our students worthy and contribute to their overall progress helping them secure their career.

Food being one of the necessities for living, we concentrate on the quality of the meals we provide. Our college has two food stations (cafeteria and canteen) serving quality meals to the ones hungry.

We maintain proper cleanliness, hygiene and quality of the meals and snacks we serve. The cleanliness of the kitchen and the hygiene of the cook and other staff of the kitchen are also looked after.

The medical facilities are open to the students at all hours to help them address emergencies as well. Furthermore, our faculty and staff can also seek our healthcare facility as and when required. 

The medical unit is well-equipped with all the possible medical devices, primary medicines and 24X7 power backup facilities that may be vital to address minor health issues and medical emergencies.

Medarametla Anjamma Mastan Rao College of Pharmacy (M.A.M) was established with a group of eminent academicians and professionals from different field with a mission to offer quality education with a moto to provide education to all and contribute itself to the millennium development goals. Since its inception, M.A.M. has been successful in providing quality education with state – of – art facilties and emerging as a leader in the field of pharmacy education. The mission is to train the enthusiastic students and transforming them as knowledgeable pharma   professionals to meet the society at local, national and global level. Within short time the college has been upgraded to PG level institutions. Facilities like International student exchange programme, personality development programme, IPA, APTI programmes, NSS unit, will help the students to groom themselves to international arena. Guest lecturers by experts from industry, different universities, tie up with multi-national companies, organizing and attending various national & international seminars, visit of top MNC’s and placement cells are unique features of M.A.M.(Updated)
fields.why_choose_us: Choosing a college to pursue one’s education is as much important as choosing the course. For anyone opting for pharmacy education in India, MAM college of pharmacy should be the first choice.The infrastructure of the Institute includes well-equipped laboratories, a well-stacked library, spacious lecture halls, separate  boy's and girls hostels, canteen, spacious play ground, payphones, Regular bus service enables students to communicate from the campus to the city. All this makes the college a conductive academic learning that provides students with quality education in a clean, comfortable environment.
fields.quality: The MAM College of Pharmacy is committed to empower our students to meet global challenges in Pharmacy profession through excellence in education. Our highly qualified and committed faculty is constantly exploring newer frontiers of knowledge with the intention to build quality pharmacist. We believe in  honing the overall persona of our students through excellence in academics, co curricular and extracurricular activities. We strive to develop a sense of social obligation and discipline among our students not only to make a better technocrat but also a better human being.

fields.Principal_msg:
Greetings from MAM PG College!!!

"Quality education with moral values is the most powerful weapon to change the world."

We, at MAM ensures quality education in technical development for the future generations of pharmacy. The purpose is to turn learning into earning and to convert talent into meaningful living. Moral values help in building the character which is the true essence of our goals. One of the aspects of learning is that no one can take it away from you.

Our institute impacts skills and expertise to enrich the students and mould them into intellectual pharmaceutical technocrats of the future. The institute also focuses in research & development along with academics. The institute is enriched with teaching talents in various specializations of pharmacy. Various academic & non-academic activities conducted by us helps in the overall personal, professional and social development of students.
fields.Vision: To be the leaders at the frontiers in Pharmacy education, research & practice at national level with global recognition.The Institute will impart a qualitative and world class pharmaceutical education to satisfy the various man power needs of the pharmaceutical sciences. The students will be given vigorous theoretical and  practical training to take up the responsibilities, challenges and to become responsible and civilized citizens. The students are  also encouraged to participate in co-curricular and extracurricular activities to develop their personality, creativity, communication and interpersonal skills.
